<template>
  <v-dialo
  v-model="getShow"
  persistent
  >
    <v-card>
        Hi User Profile
        <v-btn
        @click.prevent="closeUserProfile">
            close
        </v-btn>
    </v-card>
  </v-dialo>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'UserProfile',
    props:{
        showProfile:{
            type: Boolean,
            default: false,
            required: true
        }
    },
    computed:{
        getShow(){
            let localShow = this.showProfile
            return localShow
        }
    },
    methods: {
        closeUserProfile(){
            this.$emit('closeUserProfile',false)
        }
    },
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
